"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-26-Podium-uniforms-for-Team-China-at-2024-Summer-Olympics-unveiled-1uJZe0To8Ok-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Team China's podium uniforms for the upcoming 2024 Paris Summer Olympics were revealed in Beijing on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9035149957057537, \"rank\": 0.10678849108338564, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The uniforms were sponsored by Chinese sportswear brand Anta.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9914837207298314, \"rank\": 0.007957815522371089, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The traditional design of Chinese dragon elements were retained in the main colors of white and red.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The outfits are made from recycled fibers, and various eco-friendly materials, including recycled nylon and recycled polyester, were also used in the manufacturing process to reduce carbon emissions.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese athletes have been wearing uniforms with similar dragon-themed designs on the podium since the 2012 London Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9914837207298314, \"rank\": 0.007957815522371089, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Multiple athletes attended the unveiling ceremony in Beijing, including two-time Olympic men's weightlifting gold medalist Shi Zhiyong.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9035149957057537, \"rank\": 0.10678849108338564, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 959, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Zhiyong_(weightlifter,_born_1980)\", \"score\": 0.8421034060992093, \"rank\": 0.18750000000000883, \"text\": \"Shi Zhiyong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Zhiyong_(weightlifter,_born_1980)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Zhiyong_(weightlifter,_born_1980)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's going to be my third Olympics and I hope I can achieve an outstanding result,\\\" Shi said.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By the way, we have a strong team nicknamed as the 'King Squad,' so I hope everyone can pay more attention to the Paris Games and the Chinese weightlifting team.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\", \"score\": 0.8591147507395333, \"rank\": 0.1442526539625433, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\"}, {\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9914837207298314, \"rank\": 0.007957815522371089, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe that there will be multiple athletes wearing the dragon uniforms on the podium in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999988794429012, \"rank\": 1.1205584297908033e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"2024 happens to be the Year of the Dragon, so I think it's an auspicious sign,' Chinese boxer Li Qian said.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9914837207298314, \"rank\": 0.007957815522371089, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope I can wear this uniform on the top of the podium at the Paris Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1780,